# Per-session ephemera written by Second Brain hooks and /wrap skill (local-only by design).
# `**/` prefix matches at any depth (root + nested sub-projects).
# Canonical source: SB `_system/git-config/gitignore-project-journal-rules.txt`.
**/.project-journal/sessions/
**/.project-journal/watcher-nudges/
**/.project-journal/.session-*
**/.project-journal/.last-wrap-*
**/.project-journal/.last-end-*
# Workspace-delta cursor IS tracked (read by /resume Step 5.9).
!**/.project-journal/.last-snapshot.json
